in the neighborhood.

79
00:03:34,928 --> 00:03:35,762
Not people.

80
00:03:35,845 --> 00:03:40,141
We have me, who had a momentary setback,
but I'm feeling great now,

81
00:03:40,225 --> 00:03:41,226
and that was a while ago.

82
00:03:41,309 --> 00:03:43,603
